io.r2dbc.proxy.listener

Interface ProxyMethodExecutionListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ProxyExecutionListener

    public interface ProxyMethodExecutionListener
extends ProxyExecutionListener
    Listener interface called back when corresponding method on proxy is invoked. This interface extends ProxyExecutionListener interface and provides explicit before/after callback on each method on proxy.
    Since:
    0.8.3
    Author:
    Tadaya Tsuyukubo
